I got lots of feedback from the last map, fy_ice_2006. the peeps realy liked it. i have had requests for a DM version. but most of the architextural differrences i have made in this version.

the closeness of the spawn areas in Fy_ice_2006 gave thap map a crazy first rush, and an elitest with a smg could clean house. i have opeened up the middle and mooved the spawn areas farther apart. this balances it out out i think.  give me your thoughts.
